Method.name: populateRegions
Method.Implementation:
k ^NPMLBI.UkraineMapD k ^NPMLBI.UkraineMapI
#dim sc As %Status = $$$OK #dim stream As %Stream.Object = ##class(%Dictionary.CompiledXData).%OpenId(..%ClassName(1) _ "||" _ "regions").Data #dim reader As %XML.Reader = ##class(%XML.Reader).%New()
set sc = reader.OpenStream(stream, "literal") if $$$ISERR(sc) quit sc
do reader.Correlate("region", ..%ClassName(1))
#dim obj As NPMLBI.UkraineMap while reader.Next(.obj, .sc) { if $$$ISERR(sc) quit
set sc = obj.%Save() if $$$ISERR(sc) quit
set obj = "" }
quit sc

Method.name: revert
Method.Implementation:
set in = ##class(%Library.FileCharacterStream).%New() set in.Filename = "C:\Temp\1.txt"
set out = ##class(%Library.FileCharacterStream).%New() set out.Filename = "C:\Temp\2.txt"
set sc = $$$OK set i = 0 while(1) { set i = i + 1 set len = 900000 set str = in.ReadLine(.len, .sc, .eol) if $$$ISERR(sc) quit if (len < 0) quit
set len = $length(str, " ") for j = len:-1:1 { set cur = $p(str, " ", j) if (j < len) do out.Write(" ") do out.Write(cur) } } if $$$ISERR(sc) quit sc
quit out.%Save()
